data.description: Fantastic opportunity for a charming colonial in the Lomond neighborhood of Shaker! This meticulously maintained home provides a nice mix of modern amenities and classic Shaker Heights charm, including a gorgeous updated kitchen and hardwood floors throughout. The front entryway opens to a spacious and sun-filled living room that features beautiful hardwood floors! The living room is open to the updated eat-in kitchen that also features hardwood floors. Here you will find stainless steel appliances, plenty of crisp white cabinetry, and ample counterspace. At the back of the house is a bright family room with neutral carpet and sliding glass doors that overlook the backyard. A convenient half bath completes the first floor. The second floor features 4 large bedrooms, all with hardwood floors and ample closet space. You will love the spacious owner's suite that includes a large closet and an updated ensuite bath. An additional full bathroom completes the second floor. The finished lower level includes an updated rec room with neautral carpet and laminate flooring and a laundry room that is great for additional storage. Conveniently located just minutes from schools, parks, and the new Van Aken district! Don't miss this one!
